{"tid":1495342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] 824機場點解要早上7點","createTime":"2019-08-22T04:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T12:37:49.000Z","uid":147785,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ae5236929f18294a95077692b3b9cce37c2a60a4","tid":1495342,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:28:00.000Z","msg":"Q: 如果有禁制令延長，點算好？<br />\nA: 禁制令只係禁止入機場範圍，我地唔會進入客運大樓。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 咁到底今次點運作以達至塞到機場？<br />\nA: 我地係用盡各項方法去機場，例如渣車/坐巴士/機鐵甚至的士。只要流量夠就塞到。你有無見話朝早屯公塞到成個大西北無路走而被人告惡意堵路？<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點解要倒塔咁早？<br />\nA: 因為朝早係貨機同遠程機較多，影響較深遠。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 我咁早起唔到身點算好？<br />\nA: 今次活動係會係朝早無限輪迴形式進行，你幾點起到身都可以參加（當然準時更好）<br />\n<br />\nQ: 當日仲有觀塘遊行，怕唔怕𠝹人？<br />\nA: 一個上晝一個下晝，唔存在𠝹人。而且兩邊風險唔一樣，目標對象唔一樣。大家可以考慮風險再參加。當然大家可以走足兩場。<br />\n<br />\n由於我見直至琴日 大家對於7點塞機場仲係意見不合 所以想嘗試統一個搞手既意見<br />\n<br />\n以上Q&amp;A係由 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">和你塞公海 @stuckwithyou</span></span> group內發出 <strong>大家可以入左去睇下詳情先</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">懶人包:</span></span><br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">早上7點係for 有車既人</span></span> 早起去塞公路 阻止貨運(有貨運巴打指出 貨運係7點開始) 期望係8點塞到 <br />\n2. 唔想咁早起既人 可以8,9點搭機鐵無限loop 屆時可以睇下早上7點既車手成唔成功再考慮出門<br />\n3. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">唔入客運大樓 所以唔存在禁制令問題</span></span><br />\n4. 12點散唔係硬限制 如果仲想繼續塞 可以選擇留低 唔想則自行轉場<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8da640ba0013f9070996878a8d46d287ee5ad3","tid":1495342,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4346ede3d90c68e50af6245799a47b5a5eaa2661","tid":1495342,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:31:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21ac963bb7e4647e07f6cafca64ac74e77130888","tid":1495342,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:32:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2d4a27c7073302674c5ee9367a4032b1b1139633","tid":1495342,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:35:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b2cc4b5c544abc764b1c4c27c5fb0ac3ddc15b1b","tid":1495342,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:38:56.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"12a688501efa39dcbd1f2c5e558f7db4c2b5ed79","tid":1495342,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:55:54.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"5dc582478d2ddb3359303f75a3bd7097f659494c","tid":1495342,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"d845958130aaa2392a22d7352980cae418c1c805","tid":1495342,"uid":35484,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:58:28.000Z","msg":"大家幾時先肯行動升級搞機場？<br />\n搞機場唔單只係搞到香港經濟，亦搞到全世界經濟<br />\n有機場巴絲亦指出，停飛一日全世界要2,3日善後<br />\n大家幾時先肯齊心搞呀？<br />\n唔係搞一日就算 係要成日搞<br />\n港共想攬炒唔志在香港蝕少少 但你覺得咁多受影響既外國公司想唔想蝕？<br />\n全世界陪葬既時候，你覺得啲大國會唔會出聲？<br />\n<br />\n重點係癱瘓機場交通，唔係塞爆機場入面<br />\n空管巴絲返唔到工，航班升降效率低左就會開始delay/cancel架喇"},{"pid":"6260f61616c9cb045ffaa0c21703fa6749090916","tid":1495342,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:01:00.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"12b5d2b5e6d84900a5009341930a3719dd1797dd","tid":1495342,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff19241b4c3d034a213a7329041a74fe0311827","tid":1495342,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:03:32.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"34753788c65897b2e09feb77668a329fe5bdd8ee","tid":1495342,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:05:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">機鐵默站<br />\n機場巴士上車唔落車<br />\n東涌自駕遊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n記住帶喼"},{"pid":"70adeae11f062e38ea86370c224c03098e5fb5b3","tid":1495342,"uid":133166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:08:22.000Z","msg":"Q: 點解要倒塔咁早？<br />\nA: 因為朝早係貨機同遠程機較多，影響較深遠。<br />\n<br />\n講真, 如果貨機的話前一晚一早交曬貨入terminal , 你就算塞出面都唔會影響到, 因為貨機係照樣會夠貨起飛. 就好似上兩次cancel 機咁都只係cancel 客機. 對貨運黎講最多係本身plan 上客機嘅貨要轉貨機走, 對空誶影響真係唔太大.<br />\n<br />\n相反, 如果星期6旁晚開始搞, 咁就連日, 一機嘅貨運都會有影響.<br />\n<br />\n所以我真心唔明點解要朝早<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9266d37d89f2e4f50728570b90371c32c4d7dc3","tid":1495342,"uid":217441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"039773e0b3ec1b10a5b1ea5f184643da2853591c","tid":1495342,"uid":23271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1defb0b245cbded70940cbc3cacb786a34ad196f","tid":1495342,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:13:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad526cfbda54f13bf5b915b9c9336d7d1d138c60","tid":1495342,"uid":82183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:17:15.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"2049f36cd2dee790e5c5aa5ef17aa83578a234d0","tid":1495342,"uid":82183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dDQB1m8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdDQB1m8.jpg&h=e8343ea7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5789e35cd582803d04c07f5a1bbc34ad23c63dbb","tid":1495342,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:22:38.000Z","